text: mattu allahanu nimagagi nim'malagindale jotegalannu srstisidanu hagu a nim'ma jotegala mulaka nimage makkalannu mom'makkalannu nididanu mattu avanu nimage sud'dhavada jivanavasyaka vastugalannu nididanu. (Higirutta) avarenu asatyavannu nambuttareye? Mattu allahana anugrahagalannu allagaleyuttareye
